Rectangle Rounded Profile Definition
====================================



```
concept {
    IfcRoundedRectangleProfileDef:ProfileType -> IfcProfileTypeEnum
    IfcRoundedRectangleProfileDef:ProfileName -> IfcLabel
    IfcRoundedRectangleProfileDef:Position -> IfcAxis2Placement2D
    IfcRoundedRectangleProfileDef:XDim -> IfcPositiveLengthMeasure
    IfcRoundedRectangleProfileDef:YDim -> IfcPositiveLengthMeasure
    IfcRoundedRectangleProfileDef:RoundingRadius -> IfcPositiveLengthMeasure
    IfcAxis2Placement2D:Location -> IfcCartesianPoint
    IfcAxis2Placement2D:RefDirection -> IfcDirection
}
```
